p.k: When Scooby and the gang are hired to escort a supposedly possessed ventriloquist dummy to the annual Ventriloquist Talent Competition they meet up with the two judges of the competition Jeff Dunham and Darci Lynne Farmer. True to form the supposedly possessed dummy turns out to be terribly-and-horribly-possessed! It comes alive and attacks the competition! Can our gang join forces with our famous ventriloquist judges and their dummies / puppets in order to stop the horrible monster?
